01:39.933 --> 01:44.705 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: In the day's other
news: Authorities
in Michigan say the man accused
in Kalamazoo,

01:44.805 --> 01:50.811 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
