didn't enter
a plea. Police say Dalton killed
six people

01:56.149 --> 02:01.321 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
at random in three separate
locations Saturday
night around Kalamazoo.

02:01.421 --> 02:05.425 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
The local prosecutor said today
he's acknowledged
his role, but given no reason.

02:05.525 --> 02:10.564 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFF GETTING, Kalamazoo County
Prosecutor:
I have described this previously
as intentional,

02:10.664 --> 02:20.574 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
as deliberate, as cold. This
wasn't a -- just
a momentary lapse. This wasn't
just a crime.

02:20.674 --> 02:25.645 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
There was nothing that provoked
this. There
is videotapes of these
incidences. He walked

02:25.746 --> 02:27.714 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
