them.

02:27.814 --> 02:32.986 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: Dalton is a driver
for the ride-sharing
service Uber. Investigators are
checking reports

02:33.086 --> 02:35.389 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
