between the attacks.

02:35.489 --> 02:40.861 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
JUDY WOODRUFF: The Obama
administration today
defended its handling of a North
Korean call

02:40.961 --> 02:45.699 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
