upper-caste Jats.

04:29.102 --> 04:35.075 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MAN (through translator): The
generation of
the Jat community is in danger
of losing out.

04:35.175 --> 04:38.879 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
We are demanding hope for the
younger generation.
The government should
immediately make us

04:38.979 --> 04:41.248 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
part of the quota system.

04:41.348 --> 04:47.187 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JONATHAN MILLER: After days of
negotiations,
Jat community leaders have, it
seems, a forced

04:47.287 --> 04:55.629 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
capitulation. The Haryana state
minister promised
to table legislation to include
Jats in the

04:55.729 --> 04:58.865 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
caste quota system.

04:58.965 --> 05:06.139 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
And the federal interior
minister has ordered
that a high-level committee be
set up to address

05:06.239 --> 05:07.941 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
the Jats' grievances.

05:08.041 --> 05:12.212 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
GWEN IFILL: The water service is
now expected
to resume tomorrow. But it could
take days

05:12.312 --> 05:16.883 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
to remove vehicles left blocking
highways
and to restore rail service.

