trying it.

44:20.491 --> 44:26.964 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JACKIE JUDD: Dr. Schiffman
concedes that turning
to elephants for a cancer
treatment is outside

44:27.064 --> 44:33.437 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
the box, but that, he says, is
