44:59.797 --> 45:06.037 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: A community
organizer in a
burned-out building, a young
girl taking a

45:06.137 --> 45:12.910 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
ballet lesson, photographs of
Puerto Rican
life in New York and around the
country. They

45:13.010 --> 45:16.213 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
