the bus.

47:21.605 --> 47:23.674 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MARTIN ESPADA: He said it was
the best week
of his life.

47:23.774 --> 47:25.509 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: The best week?

47:25.609 --> 47:27.645 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MARTIN ESPADA: The best week of
his life,
because he figured out what to
do with the

47:27.745 --> 47:29.580 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
