American Art
Museum, where Martin and I met
recently.

48:03.581 --> 48:09.420 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MARTIN ESPADA: I remember this
one. This is
a photograph that was taken in
Hartford. At

48:09.520 --> 48:14.558 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
