in that photograph.

48:29.907 --> 48:35.479 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: In a poem titled
"Mad Love,"
Martin Espada refers to specific
photographs,

48:35.579 --> 48:38.916 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
