the cards,

49:11.382 --> 49:17.822 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
not the face half-hidden by the
star in the
Puerto Rican flag, the darkness
of his dissident's

49:17.922 --> 49:19.723 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
eye.

49:19.824 --> 49:26.463 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
"Now that my father cannot
speak, they wait
their turn to testify in his
defense, witnesses

49:26.564 --> 49:29.266 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
to the mad love that drove him
to it."

49:29.366 --> 49:34.004 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: You say in last
lines here,
"Now that my father cannot
speak."

49:34.104 --> 49:35.172 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
MARTIN ESPADA: Yes.

49:35.272 --> 49:37.141 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
JEFFREY BROWN: You feel a
responsibility to
speak?

49:37.241 --> 49:39.109 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
MARTIN ESPADA: Absolutely.

49:39.210 --> 49:45.583 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
