word. He can never snap another
photograph.

49:45.683 --> 49:53.457 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
That's over. And so now comes my
turn. Now
I must speak for him. And now
those faces,

49:53.557 --> 49:56.994 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
