50:26.090 --> 50:30.995 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
One-hundred-and-six-year-old
Virginia McLaurin
never thought she would live to
see a black

50:31.095 --> 50:35.599 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
president in the White House.
When she was
honored for her volunteer work
in Washington,

50:35.699 --> 50:42.640 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
