her dream was
to meet President Obama. After
an online campaign,

50:42.740 --> 50:48.279 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
McLaurin was able to fulfill her
dream, and
even dance with the president
and first lady.

50:48.379 --> 50:51.882 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The White House shared the
moment in this
video it released on social
media.

50:51.982 --> 50:53.717 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
BARACK OBAMA, President of the
United States:
Virginia McLaurin?

50:53.817 --> 50:54.418 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
VIRGINIA MCLAURIN, Volunteer:
Hi!

50:54.518 --> 50:55.152 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
BARACK OBAMA: How are you?

50:55.252 --> 50:56.186 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
VIRGINIA MCLAURIN: I'm fine.

50:56.287 --> 50:57.354 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
BARACK OBAMA: Oh, it's so nice
to see you.

50:57.454 --> 50:58.389 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
VIRGINIA MCLAURIN: It's an
honor. It's an
honor.

50:58.489 --> 50:59.056 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
BARACK OBAMA: You want to say hi
to Michelle?

50:59.156 --> 51:00.391 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
VIRGINIA MCLAURIN: Yes!

51:00.491 --> 51:01.759 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
BARACK OBAMA: Slow down now.
Don't go too
quick. She's 106!

51:01.859 --> 51:02.960 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MICHELLE OBAMA, First Lady: No,
you are not.
You are not 106.

51:03.060 --> 51:03.794 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
BARACK OBAMA: Well, you got to
-- you, slow
down.

51:03.894 --> 51:04.561 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
MICHELLE OBAMA: Oh, my goodness.

51:04.662 --> 51:05.996 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
VIRGINIA MCLAURIN: Thank you.

51:06.096 --> 51:06.730 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MICHELLE OBAMA: You are not -- I
