like you when I grow up.

51:06.830 --> 51:07.164 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
VIRGINIA MCLAURIN: You can.

51:07.264 --> 51:08.065 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
(LAUGHTER)

51:08.165 --> 51:09.199 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
BARACK OBAMA: She's dancing.
Come on.

51:09.300 --> 51:10.401 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
So, what's the secret to still
dancing at
106?

51:10.501 --> 51:11.402 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
VIRGINIA MCLAURIN: Just keep
moving. I am
so happy.

51:11.502 --> 51:13.270 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
MICHELLE OBAMA: We are happy to
have you.

51:13.370 --> 51:14.805 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
VIRGINIA MCLAURIN: A black
president.

51:14.905 --> 51:16.941 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
MICHELLE OBAMA: Look at him,
right there.

51:17.041 --> 51:18.676 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
VIRGINIA MCLAURIN: A black wife.

51:18.776 --> 51:20.911 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
MICHELLE OBAMA: That's me.

51:21.011 --> 51:22.579 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
VIRGINIA MCLAURIN: Yes.

51:22.680 --> 51:23.948 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
(LAUGHTER)

51:24.048 --> 51:28.118 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
VIRGINIA MCLAURIN: And I'm here
to celebrate
black history.

51:28.218 --> 51:30.888 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
BARACK OBAMA: That's exactly
right.

51:30.988 --> 51:35.359 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
VIRGINIA MCLAURIN: Yes. That's
what I'm here
for.

51:35.459 --> 51:40.331 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
BARACK OBAMA: Well, we're glad
to have you
here.

51:40.431 --> 51:54.144 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: I want to know
